cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the challenges of adversarial attacks and large neural network size in deep learning, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a new pruning technique that integrates robust learning objectives, which falls under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
